description: “I’m the wrestler, ready to kick some ass…” It was time for some friendly outdoor wrestling, and Frankie looked at Barron with hungry eyes, “This one right here!” I don’t know about kicking ass, but Frankie sure pounded ass! Little did Barron know, he was in for a wild ride, but he welcomed it with open arms…or rather, an open ass! Frankie dominated Barron in more ways than one, but nobody was complaining. Our twink bottom was left just as satisfied as his aggressive top when all was said and done!
title: Frankie & Barron: Bareback
